---
import SectionContainer from "./SectionContainer.astro"

 const personalImageAlt = "Alejandro Mejia"
---
<SectionContainer>
  
  <header class="text-white">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center py-8">Blog de Ciberseguridad</h1>
  </header>

  <article class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-300 bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl md:flex-row w-full max-w-4xl transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400">🚀 Level Up Your CTF Game with My Fast Port Scanner!</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Welcome to the fast lane! In the high-stakes world of Capture The Flag (CTF) competitions, every second matters. That's why my **Fast Port Scanner** is your secret weapon, designed for those of us running on limited resources. 
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        **Why settle for traditional tools like Nmap** that can weigh down your system? My scanner is optimized for speed, utilizing smart concurrency techniques that ensure you get quick results without draining your laptop’s resources. Perfect for those late-night hacking marathons or intense CTF battles!
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        Imagine scanning entire networks at lightning speed! ⚡ My script enables you to conduct high-speed scans without lag, so you can focus on what really matters: finding vulnerabilities and securing points. Whether you're on an entry-level machine or a more powerful setup, this tool is engineered for performance.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        🚀 With a simple command-line interface, you can initiate scans effortlessly. Customize your scan parameters with ease and gain the flexibility to adapt to every CTF challenge. Think of it as your customizable toolkit—ready for action whenever you are!
      </p>
  
      <p class="mb-4">
        **Quickly identify open ports** to gather critical intel on services running on a target. This information is a game-changer, helping you strategize your next move and capitalize on weaknesses faster than ever. 📈
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        Plus, I’ve built in extensive logging features so you can analyze your scans post-competition. Learn from each CTF and fine-tune your strategies for the next challenge. The faster you scan, the quicker you can adapt and conquer! 🏆
      </p>
  
      <p class="mb-4">
        So why wait? Let’s push the boundaries of what’s possible in cybersecurity together! Your feedback is invaluable, and I’m always excited to hear how we can enhance this tool. Join me on this journey to make the web a safer place, one fast scan at a time! 🔍
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <img width="100" height="100" src="/profilePic.jpeg" alt="Alejandro Mejia" class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-80 p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 rounded-2xl bg-black/30 ring-1 ring-green-500/70 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105" style="object-position: 50% 50%">
  </article>
  
  
  
  
  
</SectionContainer>
